sing both the client-toolkit and fontconfig-rs will get a cargo multiple native link error.\r\n\r\nAre titled windows something you think would be nice to have BasicFrame support or do you think its too complex?\r\n\r\n- [x] Better selection of window fonts (using gsettings and kde equivalent to find default window title font) (wont fix for the time being)\r\n- [ ] Have the title shrink to 'part_of_title...' (for example 'alacrit...') instead of completely disappearing\r\n- [x] Try to remove fontconfig-rs dependency\r\n- [x] Investigate rusttype '.otf' support (going to just use '.ttf' for now)", "created_at": "2018-09-17T10:20:45Z", "updated_at": "2018-10-08T14:16:31Z", "closed_at": "2018-10-08T14:16:31Z", "merged_at": "2018-10-08T14:16:31Z", "merge_commit_sha": "3e9a77fd3819a9c1df87976d79f7ebda10385c4b", "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "requested_reviewers": [], "requested_teams": [], "labels": [], "milestone": null, "draft": false, "commits_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Smithay/client-toolkit/pulls/35/commits", "review_comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Smithay/client-toolkit/pulls/35/comments", "review_comment_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Smithay/client-toolkit/pulls/comments{/number}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Smithay/client-toolkit/issues/35/comments", "statuses_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Smithay/client-toolkit/statuses/098c626d854607d2e3687ff168d6b09bf034599b", "head": {"label": "trimental:titled-windows", "ref": "titled-windows", "sha": "098c626d854607d2e3687ff168d6b09bf034599b", "user": {"login": "trimental", "id": 40879396, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjQwODc5Mzk2", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/40879396?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/trimental", "html_url": "https://github.com/trimental", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/trimental/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/trimental/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "ht